data.text:
When it comes to construction, there’s not much we don’t know

EKE-Rakennus Oy is a Finnish, family-run company founded in 1961 and part of the multifaceted EKE Group. EKE-Rakennus has grown from an engineering firm specialising in structural engineering into a major operator in the construction sector, covering a range of expertises. Today, EKE-Rakennus remains a family-run company, where its entrepreneurial spirit brings a personal touch and ownership that is dedicated to the long-term development to the company’s operations.

New apartment block homes for sale

WELCOME TO YOUR NEW HOME

We have a range of keenly-anticipated new homes that have now been completed, so all that is left is for you to move into your dream home.

Asunto Oy Piispanportin Aura’s modern apartment block homes are located on a dedicated plot in Espoo’s Olari district, offering easy access to a wide range of services. Dreaming of city living? Asunto Oy Töölön Castellum in Helsinki offers fantastic city homes in the pleasant Taka-Töölö area. Find out more about the homes ready and waiting for their new owners, and find your perfect apartment!

HOMES FOR SALE

EKE City – city living at its best

EKE City offers unique solutions for city living, with central locations, prestigious areas, and comprehensive transport connections.

EKE City embraces the local area, centred around a genuine respect for the environment and pace of life of the neighbourhood. We built modern homes that meet the needs, desires and requirements of today, offering architecture that honours the features that make the area what it is, blending in seamlessly with the surrounding cityscape. EKE City sites are developed around the idea of city living, where urban life, with its comprehensive services, forms a substantial part of residents’ everyday life.

Helsinki’s wonderful new homes in the Asunto Oy Töölön Castellum development have been completed in the pleasant Taka-Töölö neighbourhood.

BUYING YOUR FIRST HOME?

Tips for first-time buyers

Dreaming of owning your first home? Congratulations! You’ve already made the first step on a journey ending with a unique home tailored to your needs and preferences. Whether modern minimalism or cosy sprawl are your style, you need the right kind of framework to make your dream a reality. Take a look at the tips below to find out what you should bear in mind when looking for and buying your first home.
